Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.79,0:00:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在在你眼前  有着无限的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.35,0:00:17.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照亮了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.01,0:00:21.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海底两万哩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.19,0:00:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌懦弱的人  无法背叛蓝天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.28,0:00:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在作梦之前  我想翱翔天际
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.45,0:00:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心中的音乐盒开启  发出声响
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.34,0:00:51.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点一滴演奏出幸福与勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.76,0:01:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在在你眼前  有着无限的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.44,0:01:05.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言语是永远的信号
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.77,0:01:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't  forget  to  try  in  mind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.73,0:01:16.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱比宝石
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.62,0:01:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更能照亮一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.11,0:01:29.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时值西元1889年
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.25,0:01:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在巴黎万国博览会上认识的\N强、娜蒂亚与大王
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.48,0:01:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一同前往强在勒阿弗尔的家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.75,0:01:40.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是企图夺取"蔚蓝之水"\N的邪恶三人组
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.79,0:01:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶着万能战车·葛兰坦\N再度找上门来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.53,0:01:48.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强他们搭乘自己制作的飞机\N好不容易逃了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.63,0:01:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜引擎故障\N只好迫降在海上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.94,0:01:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亚的"蔚蓝之水"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.24,0:01:57.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟隐藏着什么样的秘密呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.54,0:02:04.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,#03  神秘大海兽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.30,0:02:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强,再这样下去会沉的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.37,0:02:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才会像这样\N尽全力在排水啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.51,0:02:39.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在明明忙到想跟猫借手来用了\N(意指"忙得团团转")
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.92,0:02:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强,那个是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.77,0:03:01.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是战舰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.94,0:03:07.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.98,0:03:10.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前方发现遇难者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.28,0:03:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.45,0:03:16.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引擎停止,右舵15度
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.13,0:03:25.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-副舰长,准备救助遇难者\N-是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.83,0:03:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们要停下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.23,0:03:32.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们有救了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.27,0:03:40.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好壮观
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.28,0:03:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧?只有你们两个吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.98,0:03:48.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.78,0:03:51.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一只狮子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.29,0:03:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.36,0:03:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有办法过来吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.59,0:03:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.39,0:03:59.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过,你这艘船还真怪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.46,0:04:01.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样根本跑不快喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.56,0:04:03.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦,这是飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.50,0:04:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞机?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.87,0:04:08.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞机是指在天上飞的那个吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.93,0:04:40.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧,坐着就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.50,0:04:41.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.17,0:04:44.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎你们来到亚伯拉罕号
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.51,0:04:46.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是舰长梅比鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.24,0:04:48.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是副舰长,赫兰少校
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.54,0:04:50.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您,梅比鲁舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.05,0:04:52.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏您,我们才能得救
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.48,0:04:55.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不着道谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.38,0:04:57.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只是军人的本分
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.49,0:05:00.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了,那架航空器是你做的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.92,0:05:03.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的,是我和姑丈一起做的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.29,0:05:05.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.46,0:05:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们对航空器也颇有兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.53,0:05:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以让我们做点调查吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.20,0:05:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.47,0:05:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.30,0:05:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.87,0:05:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.37,0:05:20.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就请你们说说\N为什么会漂到这里来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.91,0:05:22.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.89,0:05:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大致上我已经了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.49,0:05:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个三人组\N想对你们不利是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.03,0:05:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的,舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.90,0:05:43.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然追着这样的孩子到处跑\N真是群过份的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.27,0:05:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来有人在谈论我们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.40,0:05:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-一定是在谈论人家的美貌\N-一定是在谈论我的美貌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.67,0:05:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桑森
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.78,0:05:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"美丽"这个词
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.88,0:05:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了我而存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.15,0:06:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不,是为了我而存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.49,0:06:08.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都快要进入20世纪了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.66,0:06:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-还在争这种没意义的事情\N-你少多嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.93,0:06:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们有时间说这个的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.86,0:06:18.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不快去把那架飞机找到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.93,0:06:19.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-您说的是\N-您说的是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.64,0:06:23.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨好像停了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.87,0:06:26.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,天气真好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.91,0:06:29.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.75,0:06:33.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了对付海兽\N而出动的美国战舰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.55,0:06:34.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.85,0:06:39.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君子不近刑人\N危险远离,危险远离
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.62,0:06:43.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那架飞机…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.53,0:06:45.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是"蔚蓝之水"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.69,0:06:47.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.23,0:06:49.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再过三天我们会折返法国一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.93,0:06:51.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时就让你们下船吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.07,0:06:54.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您,梅比鲁舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.40,0:06:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我第一次登上战舰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.34,0:06:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以四处参观吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.74,0:07:02.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧,尽管去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.81,0:07:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.88,0:07:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-艾尔顿\N-是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.02,0:07:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由你负责照顾这些孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.98,0:07:09.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.92,0:07:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姊头
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.22,0:07:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的要跟战舰硬拼吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.89,0:07:20.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还用说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.43,0:07:23.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是为了要得到\N"蔚蓝之水"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.01,0:07:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰尾左舷有船只接近
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.84,0:07:35.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.88,0:07:42.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那些孩子说的铁制船
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.45,0:07:45.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,副舰长,去找孩子们过来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.69,0:07:47.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉他们客人到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.19,0:07:48.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.26,0:07:50.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到舰桥去是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.39,0:07:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对,舰长找你们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.53,0:07:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.07,0:07:59.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒的船喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.84,0:08:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾尔顿先生\N这艘船的全长是多少?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.31,0:08:11.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事是军事机密
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.08,0:08:17.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亚,你怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.22,0:08:18.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以参观舰桥喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.22,0:08:21.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战舰是用来杀人的船
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.49,0:08:23.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到这种东西\N竟然高兴成那样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.56,0:08:24.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太不正常了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.50,0:08:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.77,0:08:38.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.54,0:08:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的客人到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.55,0:08:49.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的耶,是葛兰迪丝小姐他们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.08,0:08:51.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然还追到海上来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.35,0:08:52.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧,副舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.19,0:08:55.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给他们两三发炮弹打声招呼\N顺便警告他们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.42,0:08:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可当作演习
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.99,0:08:59.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是,主炮发射准备
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.06,0:09:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主炮发射准备
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.93,0:09:10.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姊头\N我想再离远点会比较安全
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.21,0:09:11.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说那是什么话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.31,0:09:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是距离再拉开就追不上了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.74,0:09:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过,性命要紧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.91,0:09:17.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.95,0:09:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是贪生怕死\N岂能当得了坏蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.42,0:09:22.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是为了"蔚蓝之水"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.70,0:09:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么东西?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.10,0:09:37.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最新型的旋转炮塔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.40,0:09:39.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以水压驱动大炮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.47,0:09:41.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了不起的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.14,0:09:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-不妙\N-不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.34,0:09:52.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然开炮太过份了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.55,0:09:54.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对坏人不需要手下留情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.99,0:10:01.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好过份的船,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.09,0:10:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桑森、韩森,准备应战
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.72,0:10:03.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-收到\N-收到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.34,0:10:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.22,0:10:38.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的葛兰坦竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.98,0:10:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白旗,快举白旗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.71,0:10:58.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.05,0:11:00.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说那什么话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.35,0:11:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,性命要紧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.26,0:11:13.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始就该这么做了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.13,0:11:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,副舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.80,0:11:15.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.00,0:11:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用吊臂把他们吊起来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.40,0:11:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一到法国就交给警方查办
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.07,0:11:20.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.00,0:11:23.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-真可怜\N-真可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.61,0:12:40.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢招待
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.55,0:12:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经吃完了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.98,0:12:43.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速度真快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.95,0:12:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,因为肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.42,0:12:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且好好吃喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.22,0:12:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就多谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.33,0:12:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会转告伙房的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.43,0:12:55.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪了,这不是你做的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.96,0:12:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不,怎么会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.67,0:12:59.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然看不太出来\N但我可是位学者喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.80,0:13:01.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学者?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.20,0:13:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是身负\N美利坚合众国总统的秘密任务
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.17,0:13:09.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此搭上这艘军舰的\N海洋学家,艾尔顿博士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.41,0:13:12.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这艘船上地位仅次于舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.01,0:13:15.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你才没有穿军服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.02,0:13:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.69,0:13:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了,强
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.22,0:13:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的生物都能分为两种
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.76,0:13:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃的,跟难吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.00,0:13:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至于这条鱼…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.60,0:13:31.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,属于好吃的那一类
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.94,0:13:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.51,0:13:41.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你几乎都没吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.98,0:13:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.41,0:13:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?不吃?\N如此美味的食物?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.32,0:13:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亚,那真是太不幸了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.82,0:13:53.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人的一生就是吃、睡、玩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.66,0:13:54.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有这三项
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.69,0:13:57.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你竟然白白舍弃其中一项
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.83,0:14:01.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是…太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.86,0:14:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.10,0:14:07.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想杀害动物\N来成就自己的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.27,0:14:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你是素食主义者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.37,0:14:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.67,0:14:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不晓得吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.24,0:14:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是指不吃肉和鱼的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.85,0:14:19.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗?娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.68,0:14:23.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是大王在吃喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.86,0:14:29.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大王你吃没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.83,0:14:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了,你们想不想知道\N这艘船的秘密任务是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.30,0:14:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以说出来吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.17,0:14:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你们答应不说出去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.37,0:14:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就只告诉你们两人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.47,0:14:46.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,我答应
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.24,0:14:48.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实这艘战舰正在追捕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.58,0:14:51.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在世界各海域出没的大海兽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.75,0:14:53.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛,那我早就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.92,0:14:55.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就知道?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.15,0:14:57.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在巴黎的报纸看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.06,0:15:01.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.42,0:15:05.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过,这种事\N为什么要当成机密?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.56,0:15:07.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海兽又不会看报纸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.10,0:15:11.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之,那是军事机密
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.07,0:15:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过,有这么大艘战舰的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.60,0:15:17.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论怎样的海兽\N都不是对手啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.08,0:15:24.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是主桅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.15,0:15:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰首右舷发现疑似海兽物体
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.02,0:15:28.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正朝方位104前进
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.65,0:15:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-全舰进行海战战斗准备\N-了解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.85,0:15:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员就战斗位置
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.49,0:15:35.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复一次\N全员就战斗位置
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.33,0:15:41.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员就战斗位置…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.20,0:15:48.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.74,0:15:57.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.02,0:16:02.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.92,0:16:05.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,启航才4天就碰上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.12,0:16:07.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们实在走运
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.09,0:16:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开启所有炮门
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.46,0:16:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标为右舷大型生物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.02,0:16:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-炮击准备\N-炮击准备
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.06,0:16:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行,别开火
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.60,0:16:14.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.40,0:16:18.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是海兽也是生物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.43,0:16:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可以杀它\N太可怜了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.94,0:16:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不成
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.74,0:16:27.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙不晓得害死多少船员
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.68,0:16:28.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.85,0:16:32.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,测距完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.11,0:16:33.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有主炮开始追踪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.85,0:16:37.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方位瞄准仪至射击指挥仪\N传导正常
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.15,0:16:39.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各炮连动追针开始
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.65,0:16:42.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标距离1万2千\N速度30节
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.86,0:16:45.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,30节?这怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.26,0:16:47.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难以相信它竟然比本舰还快
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.30,0:16:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有主炮完成发射准备
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.10,0:16:53.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕,被它给逃了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.04,0:16:57.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪,好像有东西在追它
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.61,0:16:59.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它没事了是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.24,0:17:00.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.41,0:17:07.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了,给我出去!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.93,0:17:20.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪你多嘴说那些\N我们才会被赶出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.56,0:17:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来就不该杀生嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.67,0:17:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太不可原谅了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.17,0:17:26.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧,大王
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.14,0:17:33.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的\N你满脑子就只有早餐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.14,0:17:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白大王在说什么吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.14,0:17:38.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,其他动物多少也懂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.18,0:17:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我却不懂那只海兽的心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.08,0:17:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙是只邪恶的海兽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.25,0:17:47.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么可能会懂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.16,0:17:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海兽从古代就住在海中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.99,0:17:53.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是后来出现的人类\N想要猎杀海兽的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.70,0:17:56.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨,你们在吵什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.10,0:17:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海兽怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.70,0:18:00.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没看到吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.13,0:18:03.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我人在厨房,刚好错过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.71,0:18:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在厨房做什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.84,0:18:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在做要给海兽的饵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.31,0:18:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香肠是海兽的饵吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.68,0:18:15.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对,这也是军事机密
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.52,0:18:16.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂它香肠?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.02,0:18:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它又不是大王
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.62,0:18:24.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里无论什么都是军事机密
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.19,0:18:25.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是军舰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.59,0:18:26.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是没办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.99,0:18:29.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们看,这样海兽就会出现
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.64,0:18:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.57,0:18:38.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.08,0:18:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边也有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.38,0:18:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数万年前残存下来的海兽\N可不会只有一头
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.38,0:18:51.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是没有一公一母当夫妻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.19,0:18:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就生不出小孩了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.02,0:18:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来它们是夫妻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.29,0:18:57.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是海洋学家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.20,0:19:07.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.70,0:19:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潜进海里了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.97,0:19:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.87,0:19:11.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海兽是爬虫类
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.41,0:19:13.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了换气还会浮出海面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.84,0:19:15.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那边过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.75,0:19:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海兽从右舷后方接近中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.18,0:19:23.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速度32节
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.02,0:19:25.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主炮测距还没好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.79,0:19:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行,目标太过靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.12,0:19:28.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,副炮呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.92,0:19:30.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来不及
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.29,0:19:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.66,0:19:34.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行,要撞上了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.21,0:19:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真走运!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.78,0:19:52.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二管区进水
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.21,0:19:54.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注水至第三火药库,动作快
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.02,0:19:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复原倾斜\N启动右舷排水帮浦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.65,0:19:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.22,0:20:01.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这艘军舰装甲全由钢铁打造
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.49,0:20:03.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是用钢铁做成的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.16,0:20:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然能在船底开洞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.49,0:20:08.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙真的是生物吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.26,0:20:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海兽于左舷徘徊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.20,0:20:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.50,0:20:13.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右舷齐发
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.90,0:20:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要宰了它
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.95,0:20:26.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弹开了?是金属的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.21,0:20:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一头海兽呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.92,0:20:29.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在正下方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.12,0:20:36.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它在追逐那只海兽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.96,0:20:42.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船会沉吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.16,0:20:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.66,0:20:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这艘可是美国海军的\N最新战舰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.17,0:20:48.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.30,0:20:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集近代科学精华所建造出的\N亚伯拉罕号是不会沉的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.27,0:20:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海兽死了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.05,0:21:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,击中了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.32,0:21:04.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它还活着,又潜下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.15,0:21:06.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错,快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.12,0:21:07.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然会被杀死的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.06,0:21:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海兽朝舰首右舷笔直前进
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.97,0:21:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左舵,左满舵!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.00,0:21:21.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左满舵!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.34,0:21:23.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太惊人了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.10,0:21:25.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遭主炮直接命中\N竟然还能活命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.54,0:21:28.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左舷前方有物体靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.04,0:21:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.15,0:21:33.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.15,0:21:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.25,0:21:35.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是鱼雷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.13,0:21:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.24,0:21:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.24,0:21:56.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.94,0:22:01.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行,舵转不过来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.04,0:22:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左舷倾斜7度
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.48,0:22:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主炮转盘无法转动
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.25,0:22:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三、第五管区进水
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.01,0:22:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一炮塔无法旋转
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.18,0:22:08.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.88,0:22:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在太不像话了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.22,0:22:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全力进行左舷排水
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.91,0:22:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.74,0:22:38.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.25,0:22:39.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.42,0:22:44.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.62,0:22:48.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.46,0:22:49.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.72,0:22:52.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强,我找不到大王
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.99,0:22:54.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大王不见了?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.53,0:22:56.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,而且战舰也…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.70,0:23:02.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们没有注意到我们落海了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.97,0:23:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是艾尔顿…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.47,0:23:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行,你看清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.94,0:23:08.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舵被击中了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.48,0:23:10.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经无法折返了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.54,0:23:11.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.41,0:23:14.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大王
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.85,0:23:20.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大王
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.69,0:23:22.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.96,0:23:24.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大王
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.63,0:23:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满脑子就只有大王
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.43,0:23:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过,如果那真是鱼雷
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.07,0:23:39.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只海兽的真面目\N究竟会是什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.95,0:23:54.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(待续)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.72,0:24:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么应付心中的焦急才好?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.80,0:24:07.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要看不清远方的梦想了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.84,0:24:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喃喃自语  仰望星空
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.27,0:24:21.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与你的约定耀眼闪烁着
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.22,0:24:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Try  安慰的话语\N是传达不到内心的风
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.33,0:24:39.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然背负的不安逐渐膨胀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.07,0:24:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这是我自己的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.34,0:24:48.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一个人应该也不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.01,0:24:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使跌倒或感到迷惘\N仍然有明天
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.06,0:25:09.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们两个人与一只动物
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.80,0:25:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被吸进神秘大海兽的嘴巴里
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.50,0:25:14.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海兽的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.80,0:25:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实是世界上首艘实用潜水艇
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.07,0:25:20.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强,这艘船一定是海盗船
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.74,0:25:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会啦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.88,0:25:25.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发明出这么棒东西的人\N不可能会是坏人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.98,0:25:29.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海底两万哩  下一回\N“万能潜水艇鹦鹉螺号”
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.82,0:25:30.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-要看喔\N-要看喔
